SYNOPSIS

     use Lingua::ID::Nums2Words qw(nums2words nums2words_simple);
    
     print nums2words(123);        # seratus dua puluh tiga
     print nums2words_simple(123); # satu dua tiga

DESCRIPTION

    This module provides two functions, nums2words and nums2words_simple,
    to convert number to Indonesian verbage. Popular Indonesian term for
    this kind of library is "terbilang", or roughly "spelled amount" in
    English.

SEE ALSO

    Lingua::ID::Words2Nums

